I can't leave my mom.

475
00:35:06,480 --> 00:35:09,233
She's the only family
I've ever really had.

476
00:35:10,680 --> 00:35:12,591
I get it.

477
00:35:35,200 --> 00:35:38,988
Here we go, buddy.
Hours of mind-numbing escapism.

478
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:45,833
The satellite's out?

479
00:35:49,360 --> 00:35:54,673
I refuse to be denied
this one small pleasure.

480
00:35:55,800 --> 00:35:57,597
This I can fix.

481
00:36:01,800 --> 00:36:04,678
I need you. The flight's been delayed
because of the weather.

482
00:36:04,880 --> 00:36:06,757
My sister is having an anxiety attack.

483
00:36:06,960 --> 00:36:09,394
-What's the matter?
-She's superstitious and thinks...

484
00:36:09,560 --> 00:36:12,597
...this is a sign she shouldn't marry
Rodolfo. I don't know...

485
00:36:12,760 --> 00:36:14,318
...maybe a girl's point of view?

486
00:36:14,480 --> 00:36:17,790
-Sure. Yeah. Okay.
-Okay, good.

487
00:36:43,640 --> 00:36:44,993
Are you coming?

488
00:36:48,640 --> 00:36:49,914
I can't do it.

489
00:36:50,360 --> 00:36:53,591
-Okay, I'll talk to her myself.
-No.

490
00:36:53,800 --> 00:36:56,155
I mean, I can't go. I can't do this.

491
00:37:17,120 --> 00:37:21,238
The truth be told, I didn't think
you'd make it past security.

492
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:24,709
I'm really sorry.

493
00:37:27,040 --> 00:37:28,359
Can't fight fate.

494
00:38:07,320 --> 00:38:09,834
-You took the bus.
-I told you.

495
00:38:10,040 --> 00:38:11,632
Nothing was keeping me from you.

496
00:38:14,320 --> 00:38:16,197
Is it over?

497
00:38:16,720 --> 00:38:19,518
I promise you, it never started.

498
00:39:15,800 --> 00:39:18,473
Help. Anyone?

499
00:39:18,640 --> 00:39:20,119
Mom?

500
00:39:21,000 --> 00:39:23,560
Thanks for walking me.
Sure you don't want to come in?

501
00:39:23,760 --> 00:39:26,194
-The band is really good.
-Oh, no, I should get back.

502
00:39:26,360 --> 00:39:29,113
-Dishes aren't gonna wash themselves.
-Okay.

503
00:39:29,280 --> 00:39:31,589
-Bye.
-Bye.

504
00:39:46,160 --> 00:39:47,593
Hey.

505
00:39:50,360 --> 00:39:51,918
Hi.

506
00:39:54,280 --> 00:39:56,157
Are you okay?

507
00:39:59,960 --> 00:40:01,234
Yeah.

508
00:40:30,280 --> 00:40:32,032
Cohen.

509
00:40:32,800 --> 00:40:35,758
-Cohen.
-Help.

510
00:40:35,920 --> 00:40:37,797
Someone.

511
00:40:38,160 --> 00:40:40,230
Anyone.

512
00:40:41,040 --> 00:40:44,555
-Cohen?
-Summer?

513
00:40:44,720 --> 00:40:46,358
Oh, my--

514
00:40:47,720 --> 00:40:48,994
What are you doing here?

515
00:40:49,440 --> 00:40:51,032
What do you think, Cohen?

